  "body": "- [O] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\nIt seems that the nonce doesn't update for txs made in try / catch blocks, when I'm using `truffle-hdwallet-provider` as the provider.\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n1. Simple example included in the zip folder. \r\n[truffleIssue.zip](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/files/3175575/truffleIssue.zip)\r\nSample test contract: `Test.sol`\r\nSample test script: `test.js` \r\n\r\n2. Run `ganache-cli --accounts 10 --defaultBalanceEther 1000 --mnemonic 'gesture rather obey video awake genuine patient base soon parrot upset lounge' --networkId 5777 --debug` in 1 terminal\r\n\r\n3. In another terminal, CD to the unzipped folder, do `truffle test` \r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\nAll 3 test cases should have passed.\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\nOnly the first 2 test cases pass, the last doesn't because of an expected reverting tx performed in a try / catch block that causes the account nonce to be updated, but not the subsequent tx nonce.\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/12406924/57666468-99a9df80-7632-11e9-8d7c-3ddf49fd4c63.png)\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: macOS Mojave v10.14.3\r\n* Ganache version: ganache-cli@6.4.1 \r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): truffle@5.0.17 \r\n* node version (`node --version`): v11.3.0\r\n* npm version (`npm --version`): 6.4.1\r\n",
