    "body": "Nm! Thanks for the project link!\r\n\r\n`truffle-hdwallet-provider` is meant for live deployments (externally signs transactions using the account index specified). You'll notice commenting out the custom provider and setting your config like so _should_ work on your end:\r\n```\r\nmodule.exports = {\r\n  networks: {\r\n    development: {\r\n      host: '127.0.0.1',\r\n      port: 8545,\r\n      network_id: '*',\r\n      gas: 6721975,\r\n      gasPrice: 20000000000,\r\n      confirmations: 0,\r\n      timeoutBlocks: 50,\r\n      skipDryRun: true,\r\n    }\r\n  ....\r\n}\r\n```",
